  <section xml:id="sec-inference-exercises">
    <title>Exercises</title>
    <p>
      Practice exercises for the material covered in this chapter
      can be found in the accompanying
      <url href="https://worksheets.datasciencebook.ca">worksheets repository</url>
      in the two &#x201C;Statistical inference&#x201D; rows.
